Definition: a savings account deposited by someone who makes themselves the trustee for a beneficiary and who controls it during their lifetime
Example: afterward the balance is payable to the previously named beneficiary
Synonyms: savings_bank_trust, trust_account, trustee_account, Totten_trust, trust, a, savings, account, deposited, by, someone, who, makes, themselves, the, trustee, for, beneficiary, and, controls, it, during, their, lifetime, afterward, balance, is, payable, to, previously, named
Category: noun.possession
